{"tid":57730,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"食屎啦Microsoft，買surface正笨柒！","createTime":"2016-12-28T09:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T14:39:55.000Z","uid":5322,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28210ebb3d1837a8a37e2079f16fa0475f6abe3b","tid":57730,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"我就係笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n年幾前買左部surface pro3<br />\n早幾日跌爆左mon<br />\n<br />\n諗住打俾Microsoft打個價整返佢<br />\n點知Microsoft 話佢地香港無維修中心，只能俾4500換機。<br />\n<br />\nokay okay ，好合理無問題。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢又話，不過爆mon無得換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加多句，購買超過一年既機佢地唔會整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以部機變成無得整既垃圾<br />\n我知一萬幾千Microsoft don't give shit，都唔洗咁整人掛？"},{"pid":"9e81db3f9a303e82cbf9a55f83b60e3a3947eebb","tid":57730,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ms不嬲垃撚圾. <br />\n<br />\n利申用緊macbook"},{"pid":"388447bf1a8ae3031c9e0497780b956e654fa985","tid":57730,"uid":22310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"已中伏<br />\nSurface pro 4<br />\n用2個鐘冇電<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用電話好過"},{"pid":"26f8650058522085d7d38f90f1faca657138f513","tid":57730,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:31:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed675233e2e4f7316e13b37241e143affeb4ff3c","tid":57730,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩話自己笨柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我買撚左surface ，無得唔認"},{"pid":"b2d8a64f8ce51f4afeda8e5ca31f4001363da185","tid":57730,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"macbook shame"},{"pid":"8db9975bc8224f732c3aa2a644bc44bfe90ba5c0","tid":57730,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"用m$好撚慘<br />\n你想搵人屌都無，根本佢唔撚理香港市場<br />\n仲慘過對住啲廢柴genius"},{"pid":"c1ea591877c017d49e93efad723c98575fcdd154","tid":57730,"uid":59701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"我嗰陣部surface pro1，都爆過mon，嗰陣都無諗住整，係拆咗個ssd出嚟算數&hellip;&hellip;(難拆到飛起)<br />\n<br />\n依家用緊surface3，之前見ebay有部幾抵買，貪佢唔駛另外插叉電機，睇嚟要好好保護佢！"},{"pid":"58f07c4cab7e0649aaa3ebb2d8859d2a4b5d8c3b","tid":57730,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:25:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯Minecraft"},{"pid":"604f237b3cb51802b956c1d2213d75d3815125a6","tid":57730,"uid":42072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"Surface pro3壞左 <br />\n可以加錢換pro 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e802f20bc7df5712f89143a7656d57849c39b41","tid":57730,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"正評比樓主屌自己笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ee0fd372a0da56bd0f325d6de42d1b039f468b","tid":57730,"uid":56411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"我部sp3半年前個moon都自己爆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全冇跌過 係部機自爆<br />\n淨係一個角仔爆左<br />\n成部機就已經touch唔到<br />\n造工差撚到仆街<br />\n好彩保養未過 所以打去m$客服<br />\n第一次打去就俾另一個部門電話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我照打啦 打左去個人產品客户服務<br />\n傾左三個字 俾左個email佢 佢要求我send番啲單呀損毀程度圖<br />\n咁照send 啦<br />\nsend 完一日後 佢打番電話俾我<br />\n同我講我部sp3唔係個人產品<br />\n佢話係企業產品要我打番去企業個邊嘅客服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔理得咁多啦 我照打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n企業話我要cancel 左個人個邊嗰個案先可以跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟著一來一回打黎打去問 搞撚左成個月先換到機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好彩唔撚洗俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係成set 換新 不過應該都係二手機番新 仲多左一支surface pen<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"e3dd3fecbbf8e263f8d3c819125969eecc6b3a85","tid":57730,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已中伏<br />\nSurface pro 4<br />\n用2個鐘冇電<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用電話好過</blockquote><br />\n我用sp4 i7都唔止2粒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855bce0cd62ecd372c54f095cef4eb0af6b61360","tid":57730,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:13:06.000Z","msg":"官方保養得一年你買個陣唔知咁笨柒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b51f5d302d8b59230ad6f8adcf4dc571e117a16","tid":57730,"uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"真係唔好用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己之前用sp3  好彩賣到比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efca45a320486d36c5d72d0b3c2fd8303440fe2b","tid":57730,"uid":658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"過左保預左比廠吃硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎出去外邊換mon啦，香港維修部係大陸，上次拎部lumia 去整，極花個邊框唔肯認數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc195df4ea28d76d78cbd6b1ac0a39099e8d8f3","tid":57730,"uid":658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已中伏<br />\nSurface pro 4<br />\n用2個鐘冇電<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用電話好過</blockquote><br />\n我用sp4 i7都唔止2粒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二合一真係唔岩用低壓i5 最高頻都30w <br />\n要慳電真係要熄左果個自超頻技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下部買返core m 算"},{"pid":"8f1c1fe7f8268911b95103592f8bfe71c09f7e61","tid":57730,"uid":45256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"先唔撚柒講用邊粒U嘅電會有幾長命或者又有幾撚短命，SP4做工真係閪撚到震，QC班撚樣白出糧，用耐咗玻璃屏幕谷起（蝗語叫翹屏，唔好撚屌鳩我！）用手指篤會感覺輕微凹陷，此等現象熄芒用玻璃倒影反射檢查就一清二楚，先前個OS未更新睡鳩死要重新啟動先開到機呢啲不在話下，齋用chrome 上網可以每分15 分鐘扣電10％呢下係極撚品，其它問題多不勝數等其他巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 總括來講就係：Microsoft surface 系列產品推介俾仇人就最好不過"},{"pid":"f670c5394d1dabdf0fd416b1c1c64a42a0a24d62","tid":57730,"uid":41250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝"},{"pid":"5d528b8f5926f8331a571d1a948f37dd9291c50b","tid":57730,"uid":32897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"ms 垃圾<br />\n利申用緊Chromebook"},{"pid":"9cbf1aeccd3bf7dbe26066c5925c88e31d94a18f","tid":57730,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"自己整跌部機都係笨柒啲"},{"pid":"e5f6b069bd44e0f6b946a54726fa33d029b8f28c","tid":57730,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"舊屎係高登好撚多人吹奏個發佈會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b0939e4d24392427894d08f555cf4bf220e731","tid":57730,"uid":66017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:02